msgid "If you are using this router for the first time, please configure it here."
msgstr "如果您是首次使用本路由器，请在此完成基本设置。"

msgid "There are three ways to access the Internet. Please choose the appropriate one based on your network environment."
msgstr "提供三种上网方式，请根据您的网络环境选择合适的方式。"

msgid "Set the router's Wi-Fi name and password. For more advanced settings, please go to the Network > Wireless page."
msgstr "设置路由器的 Wi-Fi 名称和密码。如需更多高级设置，请进入「网络 > 无线」页面。"

msgid "LAN Settings"
msgstr "内网设置"

msgid "If these functions or services are not required, they may be disabled to conserve memory."
msgstr "如果不需要这些功能或服务，可以将其关闭以减少内存占用。"

msgid "Service Switches"
msgstr "服务开关"
